racle HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在反向代理或 WAF 层对 HTTP Basic Authentication 请求头进行长度限制（建议不超过 4096 字节），过滤包含畸形编码字符的认证请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/847"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1195","title":"NAI VirusScan NT 升级验证缺陷漏洞","description":"NAI VirusScan NT 4.0.2 在进行 FTP 在线更新病毒定义文件 scan.dat 时，由于未正确验证文件是否完整写入磁盘，即在更新流程完成后返回成功状态，导致即使病毒库文件实际未被正确修改，软件仍向管理员报告更新成功。攻击者可通过中间人攻击或控制更新服务器向目标推送无效或过时的病毒定义，使系统长期处于未受保护状态，严重影响主机安全性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1195"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.253","remediation":"升级至 Network Associates VirusScan NT 4.0.3a 或更高版本。如无法升级，可临时关闭 VirusScan 引擎后等待数秒使系统释放 scan.dat 文件句柄，再手动将最新病毒定义文件复制到 VirusScan NT 安装目录覆盖旧文件。完成操作后应通过反病毒控制台检查「Created On」日期是否已更新，以确认定义文件确实被正确替换。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92588169005196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92587579032534&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/169","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1195","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1195.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5783344e7c4adc3f449b78e346f760d75b095a9c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/169/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/151244184a2592693ea242321c22fa26af96c58c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1189","title":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator/Communicator 4.7 for Windows 95/98 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含超长参数的恶意 URL（在 `?` 后附加超长参数，引用 .asp/.cgi/.html/.pl 文件），当浏览器解析该 URL 时触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标系统拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意命令。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1189"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.500","remediation":"升级至 Netscape 4.72 或更高版本修复了该缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 Netscape 已停止维护，建议立即停止使用该浏览器，改用 Firefox、Chrome 或 Edge 等仍在支持中的现代浏览器。如无法升级，可在代理服务器或网络边缘设备上过滤包含超长参数的特殊 URL 请求。Windows 95/98 系统本身已停止安全支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36306","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/36608","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/822","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7884","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1189.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1189","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1189.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1189.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f9rc-g2vv-h5f9/GHSA-f9rc-g2vv-h5f9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ff933acb-86a6-4439-9da4-9b97189bec4f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1189.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1180","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e 及 Website Pro 2.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 args.cmd 或 args.bat 参数传递 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号等）执行任意系统命令。由于服务器未对用户输入做有效过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害较大。该漏洞影响 O'Reilly 系列 Web 服务器产品。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1180"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.360","remediation":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e/Website Pro 2.0 已停止维护，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx），并彻底停止使用旧版软件。如无法立即迁移，可在 Web 服务器前端部署 WAF 规则拦截包含 shell 元字符（如 `;`、`|`、`&`、反引号）的请求，并对 `args.cmd`、`args.bat` 参数输入进行严格白名单过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/buffer.html","http://www.tryc.on.ca/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0612.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1180","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1180.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/args_bat.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88632/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000527.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/args_bat.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1177","title":"Nph-publish 目录遍历任意文件写入漏洞","description":"nph-publish 1.2 之前版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者在文件上传操作的路径名中使用 `..`（点点）目录遍历序列，可绕过路径限制以 Web 服务器权限覆盖任意文件。攻击者可通过上传恶意脚本覆盖关键文件导致远程代码执行或服务中断，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1177"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.990","remediation":"立即升级 nph-publish 至 1.2 或更高版本（下载地址：http://stein.cshl.org/~lstein/server_publish/）。如无法升级，直接删除或移除 nph-publish 脚本的执行权限（chmod -x nph-publish）。同时确保 Web 服务器以最低权限用户（非 root）运行，并将上传目标目录权限设置为非全局可写，避免攻击者利用目录遍历覆盖任意文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-genome.wi.mit.edu/WWW/tools/CGI_scripts/server_publish/nph-publish","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2055","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1177","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1177.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-1177.yaml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx/GHSA-v755-q23g-3hrx.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1177.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/nph-publish.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1002.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1175","title":"Cisco IOS Cache Engine Web Cache Control Protocol 认证漏洞","description":"tags.<value>Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本所配套的 Cisco Cache Engine 在实现 Web 缓存控制协议（WCCP）时未引入任何认证机制。WCCP 通过 UDP 2048 端口通信，用于协调缓存引擎与路由器之间的流量重定向。由于协议缺乏身份校验，未经过认证的远程攻击者可向目标路由器的 UDP 2048 端口伪造并发送 WCCP 报文，从而将经过该设备的 HTTP 流量重定向至攻击者可控的任意主机，进而实施中间人劫持、流量监听或钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 11.2 及更早版本且启用 WCCP 功能的 Cisco 网络设备与缓存引擎，攻击只需网络可达目标 UDP 2048 端口，无需本地权限或用户交互，利用门槛低、危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1175"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.753","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.3 或更高版本以启用 WCCP 身份验证功能；若暂时无法升级，请在路由器上执行 \"no ip wccp\" 命令禁用 WCCP 服务，或在防火墙层面阻断 UDP 2048 端口防止未授权流量重定向。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-054.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/wccpauth-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1577","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1175","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1175.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4/GHSA-2qg5-3mg4-mrr4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1175.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cisco-sa-19980513-wccp-auth.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001005.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71565265-4d4c-43b5-9801-c1bbf5c6174a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0998","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1174","title":"Iomega ZIP-100 磁盘驱动器密码保护绕过漏洞","description":"Iomega ZIP-100 磁盘驱动器存在密码保护绕过漏洞，具有物理访问权限的攻击者可利用该漏洞绕过磁盘密码保护。攻击方式为：先插入已知密码的磁盘，等待驱动器断电后手动替换为目标磁盘，再用已知密码访问受保护的目标磁盘中的数据。该漏洞影响 Iomega ZIP-100 系列驱动器，需要物理接触目标设备，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1174"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.640","remediation":"由于该漏洞为 Iomega ZIP-100 硬件设计缺陷，官方已停止支持且无固件补丁。建议立即停止在涉密场景使用 ZIP-100 驱动器，改用支持硬件加密的现代存储设备；如继续使用，须对所有数据在写入前使用第三方加密软件（如 VeraCrypt、BitLocker）进行全盘加密，并确保驱动器物理存放于上锁机柜或受限访问区域，防止未经授权的人员接触。作为临时缓解措施，在驱动器使用完毕后彻底断开电源并移除数据线。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.counterpane.com/crypto-gram-9812.html#doghouse"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0998.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0997","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0997.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1168","title":"ISS Internet Security Scanner 5.3 安装脚本本地文件权限提升漏洞","description":"适用于 Linux 平台的 Internet Security Scanner (ISS) 5.3 版本的 install.iss 安装脚本在处理临时文件时存在不安全操作缺陷，未对临时文件路径进行充分校验。本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击将临时文件链接至目标系统文件，从而在安装过程中修改任意文件权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 ISS 5.3 for Linux 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1168"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.903","remediation":"安装前手动删除临时文件 `/tmp/iss.install` 并检查是否为符号链接；修改 install.iss 脚本使用 `mktemp` 创建临时文件，避免使用可预测路径；以非 root 用户执行安装程序，降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12640"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0997.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0996","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1167","title":"Third Voice Web Annotation 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"Third Voice Web Annotation 注释工具存在跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞。远程攻击者可在网页注释中注入恶意 JavaScript 代码，当其他 Third Voice 用户浏览同一页面并加载注释时，恶意脚本将在用户浏览器中自动执行，导致攻击者可窃取用户 Cookie 及敏感数据，或伪造网页内容实施钓鱼攻击。该漏洞影响 Third Voice 注释扩展所有版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。用户需警惕不明来源注释，建议卸载该软件以消除风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1167"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.783","remediation":"立即卸载 Third Voice 软件（该产品已停止维护，于 2000 年左右退出市场且不再发布安全更新）。在浏览器扩展管理中移除所有 Third Voice 相关插件。替代方案：使用现代浏览器内置注释功能或基于服务端的内容注释工具（如 Hypothes.is），这些方案默认对用户输入进行转义处理并实施 CSP 策略，可有效防范 XSS 攻击。如需继续使用第三方注释系统，应启用 Content-Security-Policy HTTP 头并配置 `script-src` 限制内联脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7252.php","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20636%2C00.html","http://www.wired.com/news/technology/0%2C1282%2C20677%2C00.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d39c6fc359564f87c4fbc1b2c3e7c679c878fdd9/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1167","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1167.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b61a9cff022af7967458616078d0be1725a7f46a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq/GHSA-qgpq-pjxc-x5wq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83040/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1167.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e64526992db40c94520d0244d04a3aa859684904/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0996.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0995","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1166","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 Segment Limit 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 版本中对于自定义段限制（Segment Limit）的编码处理存在缺陷，导致本地攻击者能够通过访问并修改内核内存来提升权限至 root。该漏洞源于内核未正确验证段限长值，使得低权限用户可利用特定系统调用绕过内存访问限制。攻击者需拥有本地系统账户并具备代码执行能力，成功利用后可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.37 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1166"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.663","remediation":"建议立即升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.38 或更高版本（如 2.2.x 系列），该漏洞在内核 2.0.38 中已修复。若无法升级，可通过限制本地用户对 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/18156","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/523","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19419"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0994","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1165","title":"GNU fingerd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"GNU fingerd 1.37 存在权限处理不当漏洞，程序在访问用户信息前未能正确放弃特权，导致本地攻击者可通过两种方式利用：一是在 .fingerrc 文件中放置恶意程序获取 root 权限；二是利用 .plan、.forward 或 .project 文件的符号链接读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 GNU fingerd 1.37 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，需手动修复或禁用 finger 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1165"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.533","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNU fingerd 至 1.37 以上版本，该版本已修复权限提升漏洞。更推荐的方案是直接禁用 finger 服务（systemctl disable fingerd 或在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释 finger 行），因为该服务在现代网络环境中已无必要且存在安全隐患。如必须使用，应限制 .plan/.forward/.project 等文件的写权限，禁止普通用户在这些文件中使用符号链接，并删除 .fingerrc 文件的可执行权限以防止恶意程序执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93268249021561&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/2478","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0993","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0667","title":"TCP/IP ARP协议缓存投毒欺骗漏洞","description":"ARP（地址解析协议）协议设计上缺乏身份验证机制，在同一广播域内的任何攻击者均可向目标主机发送伪造的 ARP 应答报文，毒化其 ARP 缓存表，将目标 IP 地址与攻击者 MAC 地址关联。该漏洞影响所有使用 ARP 协议的网络设备，攻击者无需认证即可实施中间人攻击、IP 地址欺骗或拒绝服务攻击，是局域网中最基础且广泛存在的协议层安全问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0667"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.363","remediation":"在关键网段交换机启用动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 和 DHCP Snooping，阻止伪造 ARP 报文；对核心资产配置静态 ARP 条目；部署 ARP 防火墙或 arpwatch 等监控工具检测异常 ARP 变化；使用 IPsec/MACsec 加密通信链路，降低中间人攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019797&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0990","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0990.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0664","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限提升漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统中应用程序关键注册表项权限设置不当，本地攻击者通过修改注册表内容可实现对目标系统的权限提升，获取管理员权限并执行任意操作。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 等早期版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，需限制本地用户对系统注册表的写入权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0664"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.140","remediation":"立即升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2008 及以上），Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不再发布安全补丁。如暂时无法升级，使用 Regedt32 检查 `HKLM\\Software` 下应用程序关键注册表项的权限配置，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的完全控制及写入权限，仅保留 SYSTEM 与 Administrators 组的完全控制权，并对所有敏感注册表键遵循最小权限原则进行 ACL 加固。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0664"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0990.toml"}]